# Synced rules (read-only)
Files under `.cursor/rules/synced/` are copied from the [cursor-config](https://github.com/DeanAyalon/cursor-config) repository. Do not create, edit, rename, or delete them in this project.

- To change shared standards: edit cursor-config and re-run sync
- For codebase-specific guidance: add or edit files only under `.cursor/rules/project/`
- For personal developer constraints: add or edit files only under `.cursor/rules/local/` (gitignored)

## Precedence
When guidance conflicts across tiers: **local** > **project** > **synced**
